---
title: Merge Sort  |  O(n log n) · Space O(n)
---
flowchart TD
    classDef startEnd fill:#22c55e,stroke:#15803d,color:#fff
    classDef decision fill:#f59e0b,stroke:#b45309,color:#fff
    classDef process fill:#3b82f6,stroke:#1d4ed8,color:#fff
    classDef result fill:#8b5cf6,stroke:#6d28d9,color:#fff

    A([mergeSort arr]):::startEnd --> B{"arr.length <= 1?"}:::decision
    B -- Yes --> C([Return · already sorted]):::result
    B -- No --> D["Split into leftHalf and rightHalf"]:::process
    D --> E([mergeSort leftHalf]):::startEnd
    D --> F([mergeSort rightHalf]):::startEnd
    E --> G["merge leftHalf + rightHalf into sorted array"]:::process
    F --> G
    G --> H([Done]):::result
